ara atr&aacute;s. Se encontraron aparte, muchas mejoras que excede el scope de la vulnerabilidad.<br />Today: Plasmar en un documento de confluence las mejoras encontradas. <br />Blockers? No.</p></td><td><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>7</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>incomplete</ac:task-status>\n<ac:task-body><span class=\"placeholder-inline-tasks\">Hablar con Joaco el tema de PRs y deploy.</span></ac:task-body>\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td></tr><tr><td><p><time datetime=\"2023-08-15\" /> </p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:bd6be9b3-2ff0-412b-8fb1-57e9e188f6cf\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p>Yesterday: El problema es m&aacute;s grande de lo pensado.<br />Today: Hoy va a seguir tratando de identificar el problema. <br />Blockers? Si, pero va a ayudar Joaco a destrabar.</p></td><td><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>6</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>complete</ac:task-status>\n<ac:task-body><span class=\"placeholder-inline-tasks\">Hablar con Joaco para que ayude</span></ac:task-body>\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td></tr><tr><td><p><time datetime=\"2023-08-14\" /> </p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:bd6be9b3-2ff0-412b-8fb1-57e9e188f6cf\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p>Yesterday: Investigando sobre la tecnolog&iacute;a. Joaco estuvo dando una mano.<br />Today: Esta semana cerrar el fix de Tpago. Hoy va a seguir investigando.<br />Blockers? No.</p></td><td><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>5</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>incomplete</ac:task-status>\n<ac:task-body><span class=\"placeholder-inline-tasks\">Mi&eacute;rcoles, tratar de tener el problema detectado.</span></ac:task-body>\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td></tr><tr><td><p><time datetime=\"2023-08-10\" /> </p></td><td><p><ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:bd6be9b3-2ff0-412b-8fb1-57e9e188f6cf\" /></ac:link> </p></td><td><p>Yesterday: Error 1 de Tpago, lo pudo replicar. Aprendiendo de frameworks y set up del proyecto. <br />Today: Seguir analizando Tpago y commerce-suite.<br />Blockers? No.</p></td><td><ac:task-list>\n<ac:task>\n<ac:task-id>2</ac:task-id>\n<ac:task-status>incomplete</ac:task-status>\n\n</ac:task>\n</ac:task-list></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2675966020"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":499142493},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2675966020/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2675966020/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2675966020/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2675966020/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2675966020","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2675966020/Vulnerabilidades+Daily+Sync","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2675966020","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2675966020","tinyui":"/x/RACAnw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}